{"tid":876641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「轉載」土耳其網紅「撒鹽哥」餐廳表演失控釀災","createTime":"2018-10-25T17:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T18:33:32.000Z","uid":6640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7b6ce6f4b089581d00e0ed25ac42d0d2844c09","tid":876641,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"據悉，撒鹽哥的餐廳「Nusret Etile」為招攬生意而安排聘請調酒師來進行特技火焰表演，事發當晚九點左右，其中一名工作人員在表演過程中發生了失誤，使得火勢突然竄起，一大團火焰延燒至圍觀的群眾，造成四名國外遊客以及兩名店員燒傷，甚至奇墜燒傷程度相當嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n事故發生一開始，所有的顧客皆圍坐火焰表演的吧台附近觀看演出，但當調酒師<span style=\"color: red;\">點燃酒精</span>的過程中，<span style=\"color: red;\">火焰竟失控</span>而騰空，火勢快速延燒到吧台旁的顧客。調酒師助手見狀即刻<span style=\"color: red;\">水倒在火焰</span>上撲滅，結果火不但沒滅，反而越燒越大。餐廳內個人與店員皆四處逃竄，尖叫聲連連，場面相當混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=IlJHWfrzNUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D10%26v%3DIlJHWfrzNUQ&d=3yIpaL2E6bo%2F5HUhI5S2uP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e1d60d0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=IlJHWfrzNUQ</a>"},{"pid":"ffdb6d3f2b62cdc48138ed19781697051ecc86cc","tid":876641,"uid":97340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"特務on J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d51e9d9c82ddc0b600f67a1f367a2af5188f6fc","tid":876641,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffdb6d3f2b62cdc48138ed19781697051ecc86cc","tid":876641,"uid":97340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"特務on J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"睇到都想笑"},{"pid":"46695386c2fc77afe31f27eb787294244ee526a5","tid":876641,"uid":21782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"啲火勁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}